{"tid":699111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(左翼奪權) 西班牙撤銷對「加泰羅尼亞」的嚴格財政控制","createTime":"2018-06-12T08:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T14:56:58.000Z","uid":134071,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e7b7866eaf38bb8e44c2d03ebd2f34ddcca83170","tid":699111,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:57:06.000Z","msg":"早前, 前西班牙首相Mariano Rajoy因不信任動議通過, 被迫下台.   <br />\n<br />\n左翼政團社會黨既領袖Pedro Sanchez則接任首相.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20180609052353\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsID%3D20180609052353&d=ZzA5IRrzd3BZ%2FN4D7BApPcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=8d45f337\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20180609052353</a><br />\n<br />\n西班牙新政府撤銷對加泰地區財政控制並尋求對話<br />\n9/6/2018 5:23<br />\n<br />\n        西班牙新政府撤銷對加泰羅尼亞的財政控制, 並與加泰地區政府尋求對話, 紓緩雙方因為獨立問題而變得緊張的關係.<br />\n<br />\n        新內閣開會後, 發言人宣佈這項消息, 又指首相桑切斯可能在夏天前, 與加泰羅尼亞地區主席托拉會面, 但無透詳情.<br />\n<br />\n        發言人表示, 加泰地區絕對不能再就獨立舉行公投.<br />\n<br />\n        上任首相拉霍伊鐵腕阻止加泰地區獨立, 在加泰地區去年10月舉行獨立公投前, 已實施財政管控, 加泰地區政府的所有開支, 都受到中央政府的嚴格審查."},{"pid":"4b63ad462dd2ab96ad8e49805f36c208c9aa3b53","tid":699111,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T09:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb2780a408d91b43c699f00f90c8459a5d1d18c","tid":699111,"uid":113000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T09:30:38.000Z","msg":"天滅霍伊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb3e2e10f5ea435952ef68bde4647013be02ca9","tid":699111,"uid":34760,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T09:31:29.000Z","msg":"一早係咁咪唔會搞到獨立公投囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2fdb6518c51688e4068393ceef73d0aa2cd865a","tid":699111,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T09:33:24.000Z","msg":"咁普依格蒙特點？"},{"pid":"f73e5bf8c6cf2633c65d9d155fe49fdd56841e7e","tid":699111,"uid":140776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T09:34:10.000Z","msg":"應該等左膠上台先搞獨立"},{"pid":"ebe2cce250321175e5643c564c0cfef1818deb56","tid":699111,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T09:58:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e221ee7797e5605a3f1b1aac6624b6fe1e6a01f","tid":699111,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T05:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734d3f2c0aa28b2539fce40fe76fa842c1f72dd2","tid":699111,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T05:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7e4e435a010355322ebc84b84f56d90e8b803e","tid":699111,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T14:56:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}